---
title: Double Middle Eastern Chicken Burger & Zesty Fries with Caramelised Onion & Garlic Hummus
description: Did you say hummus and chermoula, for burger night? The answer is yes and we can’t wait to take a big bite out of a Middle Eastern chicken burger, layered with hummus and pickled onion. If you have any garlic hummus left over, feel free to dip the zesty fries in for some fun!
